Not a scrap , cried Blount , quite carried away . 
A harlequinade's the quickest thing we can do , for two reasons . 
First , one can gag to any degree and , second , all the objects are household things tables and towel horses and washing baskets , and things like that . 
That's true , admitted Crook , nodding eagerly and walking about . 
But I'm afraid I can't have my policeman's uniform ? Haven't killed a policeman lately . 
