Shut , you see an English interior . 
Open , a moonlit garden . 
It all goes by magic . 
How even such a banquet of bosh was got ready in the time remained a riddle . 
As always happens , the invention grew wilder and wilder through the very tameness of the bourgeois conventions from which it had to create . 
