I have seen wicked things in a Turkey carpet . 
Mon Dieu ! cried Flambeau , laughing . 
They are letters and symbols in a language I don't know but I know they stand for evil words , went on the priest , his voice growing lower and lower . 
The lines go wrong on purpose like serpents doubling to escape . 
