Oh , the shape be damned ! cried Flambeau . 
What has the shape to do with it ? There were twenty three snipped papers , resumed Brown unmoved , and only twenty two pieces snipped off . 
Therefore one of the pieces had been destroyed , probably that from the written paper . 
Does that suggest anything to you ? A light dawned on Flambeau's face , and he said There was something else written by Quinton , some other words . 
